OL,6,FRay Matthews, who fundraises regularly
OL,7,Ffor the school described the thefts as
OL,8,F"absolutely disgusting".JHe said: "The
OL,9,Fimpact that this has on children from
OL,10,FNewman school is just devastating. My
OL,11,Fjob now is to come out of all that.
OL,12,F"Let's look at some sort of
OL,13,Fpositivity, let's get them new
OL,14,Fvehicles. My aim now is to set up some
OL,15,Ffundraising initiatives.JMr Matthews
OL,16,Fadded: "These children love getting
OL,17,Fout into fresh air. They can't do it
OL,18,Fon their own... We need proper
OL,19,Ftransport for them so they can get
OL,20,Fthere safe and secure."JOne of the
OL,21,Fstudents, 17-year-old Ryan, said: "We
OL,22,Fcannot do anything at the minute which
OL,23,Fis really sad because a lot of people
OL,24,Flike spending a lot of time outside of
OL,25,Fschool doing stuff like catering or
